* Copy the 'server' folder somewhere in your Web server

* Copy 'config.php.dist' to 'config.php' and edit accordingly

* If you want to use it with the ARC2 backend, download arc2 (http://arc.semsol.org/) and install it in a folder
	named 'arc' in the 'server' one

* Give your webserver read-writed to the 'feed' directory

* Depending on your type of feeds, you may want to adjust 'feed/.htaccess'

* Go to 'index.php' and start registering some queries

* To LOAD data via the interface (and launch the triggers) you can HTTP POST files to /?post=1 
